        <updateDate>2009-05-22T20:51:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Single Parent Protection Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow individual taxpayers who are entitled to receive child support a refundable tax credit for any unpaid portion of such support; and (2) increase the income tax liability of any individual required to pay child support by the amount of the unpaid child support allowed as a tax credit by this Act. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Single Parent Protection Act of 2009</title>
